 {r}←SetGlobalConfigFile new
⍝ Sets or deletes the global config file GetGlobalConfigFile `apm_config.json`.\\
⍝ If `new` is empty the global vars `GLOBAL_CONFIG_FILE` is deleted. If `new is
⍝ not empty it's used to set `GLOBAL_CONFIG_FILE`.\\
⍝ Returns the former setting of an empty vector.
 :If 2=⎕NC'GLOBAL_CONFIG_FILE'
     r←GLOBAL_CONFIG_FILE
 :Else
     r←''
 :EndIf
 :If 0=≢new
     ⎕EX'GLOBAL_CONFIG_FILE'
 :Else
     GLOBAL_CONFIG_FILE←new
 :EndIf
